{"word":"ναυκληρέω","slug":"ναυκληρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ναυκληρέω</b></el> <el>(ναυκληρέω,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to be a shipowner</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ν. πόλιν</el> <i>to manage, govern</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ναύκληρος'><el>ναύκληρος</el></a>\n"}]}